Make a Report
Reports --> New Report --> Category : All --> Search : Discoveries --> Start Report --> Update Preview Automatically slider to switch it on
--> Add column : Link , Notes --> Add group : Type --> Save
      Report Name: New Discoveries Report
      Description: Summary of my career exploration discoveries
--> Save --> Run
==============================================================================================================================
Add a Chart to the Report
Discoveries Report --> add a chart --> chart properties (Gear icon) --> Donut 
--> Chart Attributes section :  Chart Title: Discovery by Type
                                Value: Record Count
--> Save
==============================================================================================================================
Add the Report to a Dashboard
Dashboards --> New Dashboard --> 
Name: My Discoveries
Description: My career exploration discoveries dashboard --> Create --> +Component --> New Discoveries Report --> Select
--> Gauge component --> four segment ranges at 0, 5, 10, and 15 --> Add

+Component --> New Discoveries Report --> vertical bar chart component --> Add 
--> Drag the component so itâ€™s next to the gauge component --> Save and Done

